  "problemSolved": {
    "statement": "Sodium is an easy-to-use software library that provides a wide range of cryptographic operations including encryption, decryption, digital signatures, and secure password hashing.",
    "context": "Sodium is an easy-to-use software library that provides a wide range of cryptographic operations including encryption, decryption, digital signatures, and secure password hashing.\n\nIt is a portable, cross-compilable, installable, and packageable fork of [NaCl](http://nacl.cr.yp.to/). While maintaining API compatibility, libsodium extends functionality to improve usability and simplify the development of secure applications.\n\n---",
